        {
            "+content": "Loosely based on novel “The Tale of Genji Monogatari”. When the Emperor brings in a new wife to have a mother for his son, Hikaru-no-Kimi. He falls in love with her even if he can’t have her. So Hikaru's feelings roam as his body wanders from bed to bed, seeking a replacement for her. When he finds the girl he believes can take her place, he commits a terrible sin. Now, a thousand years later, Hazuki become the new life of Hikaru. However, because of Hikaru’s sin, Hazuki is cursed to shakes like a lamb when any girl touches him.",
